						               													<description>Welcome to Trifouilly-les-Oies. The fields will be replaced with a commercial zone. Your mission: save the archaeological sites from destruction. Will you be able to resist to the weather and unforeseen events? Will you finish the research in time?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Operation Arch&amp;eacute;o offers you two game modes : a &amp;quot;Family&amp;quot; mode or an &amp;quot;Expert&amp;quot; mode,  and three levels of difficulty. It is played solo and up to 6 players, from 9 years. The parts last 30 or 90 minutes depending on the desired duration. The optional web application can be used free of charge.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Operation Arch&amp;eacute;o, teamwork is at the heart of the game. Each of the six archaeologists has unique abilities. Who will you choose to incarnate? S&amp;eacute;verine the team leader and her motivation techniques? Franck the backpacker and his paternalistic advice? Raphael the resourceful? M&amp;eacute;lanie the hard to cook? Youssef the perfectionist? Ana&amp;iuml;s the ingenous?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Search the ruins left by the men of prehistoric mens, the Gallic, the Roman and the French of the Middle Ages.&amp;#10;Castles, aqueducts, houses, temples, cemeteries, churches and many more are only waiting for you to be discovered in scenarios inspired by real archaeological excavations.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
